Interface CfaEdge<CfaNodeT extends CfaNode>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JvmAssumeCaseCfaEdge, JvmAssumeCfaEdge, JvmAssumeDefaultCfaEdge, JvmAssumeExceptionCfaEdge, JvmCallCfaEdge, JvmCfaEdge, JvmInstructionCfaEdge

    public interface CfaEdge<CfaNodeT extends CfaNode>
    An edge for Cfa parametrized by its nodes CfaNodeT. A CFA edge corresponds to instructions between the offsets of its target and source.
